-- Home Depot says buys China's The Home Way
-- 
-- Wed Dec 13, 2006 4:05am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/12/13/businesspro-homedepot-acquisition-the-ho-idUSWEN108020061213

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - U.S. home improvement retailer Home 
Depot Inc. ( HD.N ) said on Wednesday it had signed an agreement 
to buy Chinese home improvement retailer The Home Way, giving 
it a retail presence in China with 12 stores in six cities. 

  Home Depot said the deal has received necessary Chinese 
government regulatory approvals and is expected to close by the 
end of the year. Terms of the deal were not disclosed.